title: Verify that the payload is displayed for the org.techbd.service.http.Interactions$RequestResponseEncountered interaction when a CSV zip file is sent to the /flatfile/csv/Bundle endpoint

steps.stepname: Click on the interactions menu header and navigate to FHIR via HTTPs tab.
Locate the most recent interaction sent.
Click on the interaction ID with the nature org.techbd.service.http.Interactions$RequestResponseEncountered.
Verify that the payload is displayed correctly.
